{"tid":1300360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對付藍種人的說話","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:00:00.000Z","uid":250301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67cf82e1e3a49044bed57b21c6a1f022e7cf16cd","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲 <br />\n明白返工有阿凡達已經好黑人僧 <br />\n如果屋企人係藍種人仲厭倦及憤怒<br />\n同時帶比你地好多負面情緒 辛苦曬 ! <br />\n<br />\n個人認為鬥屌已經無乜作用<br />\n第一影響左自身情緒 <br />\n第二可能加深佢地既憎恨<br />\n<br />\n可以咁樣同佢地講 : <br />\n唉 呢人話某國控制人民思想等等...<br />\n唔比書佢地讀 令到佢地唔識反抗 聽教聽話<br />\n我都唔信 ! (要大大聲好激動咁講)<br />\n(仲要講到好唔憤氣同好虔誠相信無呢回事)<br />\n之後再爆一句 :<br />\n唉 原來係真 大大個活生生人板係我面前 !<br />\n然後一句說話都唔洗再多講 <br />\n就算佢係咁聊你都唔洗理鳩佢<br />\n佢會自己胡思亂想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時自己唔洗再花心機精神同佢地解釋咁多<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲真係辛苦曬大家<br />\n面對阿凡達家族確實係精神上既虐待<br />\n有少許建議 ：<br />\n扮中立 唔出聲 乜都唔知 當人透明 長帶耳機同炸歌<br />\n唔好離家出走住 食窮個屋企先<br />\n日後唔比家用 就係對佢地最大懲罰 <br />\n<br />\n衷心希望大家頂得住 仲有好長時間<br />\n互相幫忙 互相扶持 互相鼓勵<br />\n香港屬於我地 未來就係我地手中 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外深信有人唔相信社會信用體系不在港實拖<br />\n有對眼都睇到留左位比香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qW0DACx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqW0DACx.png&h=b0d05acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRFID身份證<br />\n智能監控燈柱<br />\n社會信用體系<br />\n送中條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紋哂身都知咩事啦...<br />\n<br />\n香港有咩好 ? 好在有你 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a923ebdc98d3c0026088419047e4b2b124803b","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"無野講"},{"pid":"ed0765f90238c51b32419ce5989821a797083e1f","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"無野講"},{"pid":"e78c85270583aad905824680df8866ed1ff519e9","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"都話無野講"},{"pid":"988131d9ced93398ed88191485894732115aa31b","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"都話無野講"},{"pid":"8cf1dd756ab8487d44baa31015fda6afebf00ba2","tid":1300360,"uid":55028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"香港加油！"},{"pid":"1e829d52cf85367084f66a7639a3dafaf39d7c61","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"無野講"},{"pid":"0f494c525ba0fb4a04e744f3cf24a117e34b1765","tid":1300360,"uid":116785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"大家加油撐住！！今日廢老比我煩到quit group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6852c92f108be6c058613aebfa426b589b7f4326","tid":1300360,"uid":250301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f494c525ba0fb4a04e744f3cf24a117e34b1765","tid":1300360,"uid":116785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"大家加油撐住！！今日廢老比我煩到quit group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"成功既第一步"}]}